16:39.070 --> 16:40.493
What power source?

16:40.513 --> 16:41.955
Where's the electricity coming from?

16:42.015 --> 16:44.459
Who's spiritual credit card are you using?

16:44.960 --> 16:47.283
Again, we're not disputing the miracle happened.

16:47.504 --> 16:51.570
