16:51.682 --> 16:57.711
Basically, they're thinking, we've had this demonic circus before with Jesus and we got him taken out.

16:58.712 --> 17:03.920
So again, their question would hang in the air just like cigarette smoke, just wouldn't go away.

17:04.581 --> 17:11.911
