17:12.492 --> 17:19.442
The comforter, the counselor, the advocate, the spirit of truth and life, the intercessor, the greatest witness speaks now through Peter and John.

17:20.194 --> 17:26.103
Peter, filled with the Holy Spirit, said to the Sanhedrin, rulers and elders of the people.

17:27.105 --> 17:35.959
If we're being called to account today for an active kindness shown to a man who is lame and are being asked how he was healed, then know this.

17:37.341 --> 17:45.093
You and all the people of Israel, it is by the name of Jesus, who's the Messiah from Nazareth, whom you crucified.

17:45.754 --> 17:48.338
And God, Elohim, Yahweh, the great I am,

17:48.578 --> 17:53.083
God of Moses raised him from the dead that this man stands healed.

