19:18.102 --> 19:26.931
And again, sitting in 2023, most of us not having Jewish heritage, we don't understand the power, the insult of what he says next in verse 11.

19:27.692 --> 19:35.760
He says, Jesus is the stone you builders rejected, which has become the cornerstone.

19:36.681 --> 19:41.586
Okay, this is like, there is no gray here.

19:42.402 --> 19:47.709
